== Batteries and Merging Items ==
The Time Bus can have its speed increased, by inserting charged batteries into the battery slots in the engine room at night. To charge the batteries, they must be struck with lightning on the roof of the bus. Lightning can strike the bus, through the luck of a Thunderstorm event, or through the late stages of the WhiteNight boss fight.
